<head>
<title>无限剑制</title>
</head>
<body>
	<div>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;无限剑制<br>
I am the bone of my sword.<br>
吾身为剑所成。<br>
Steel is my body,and fire is my blood.<br>
血潮为铁，心为琉璃。<br>
I have created over a thousand blades.<br>
跨越无数战场，立于不败之地。<br>
Unknown to Death.<br>
未曾败退。<br>
Nor known to Life.<br>
无一知己。<br>
Have withstood pain to create many weapon.<br>
他，常独自一人立于剑丘之上，陶醉于胜利之中。<br>
Yet,those hands will never hold anything.<br>
因此，他的生涯已经失去了意义。<br>
So as I pray,unlimited blade works！
此身，已成无限之剑！
	</div>
